column6: I'm Rebo4AI; I'm a prototype conversational agent.
I'm Rebo4AI; I'm a prototype conversational agent.
You have learned in the "Introduction to Data Science and Artificial Intelligence" different definitions of intelligence; I have not been able to follow!
But I'm curious: Is a duck now intelligent or not? Why?
Are you personally satisfied with this decision and definition?
How interesting is it for you to know whether a duck is intelligent or not?
What in your life would change, depending on whether you see a duck as intelligent or not?
